Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.04,tk-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(296,227)}来吧！\N松阳祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临2年D班办亚洲咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来占一卦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:58.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 这边是恐怖馆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:01.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:03.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位来客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:08.63,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,给三位 带路 要注射了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在干什么呀 书呆女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:16.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因道路有杂物 所以请小心脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是搞什么啊 那句 要注射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这间废弃的房子以前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:34.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 有目击此屋主人欲求鲜血而在四处徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:36.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(568,62,504,60)\fs50\pos(568,62)\frz353.2\fn方正苏新诗柳楷简体\c&H46225E&\3c&H6E7069&}恋 之 泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:36.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(939,339,889,334)\fs48\fn@方正苏新诗柳楷简体\frz257.3\pos(939,339)\c&H232861&\3c&H526A64&}各种愿望都能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这个护士一点干劲都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.65,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说为什么装扮成护士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(492,92,563,81)\fs50\frz13.45\fn方正少儿_GBK\c&H3F56A0&\3c&H3D323D&\pos(492,92)}胸 部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:43.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 很让人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:56.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的致命武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们会没法搭讪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为补偿给我们介绍女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.41,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:22.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段时间因为控制不住情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间犹豫起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有什么好慌张的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:33.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春他说的太若无其事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:40.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从什么时候开始 变得这么容易动摇的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己决定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来都没有迷茫过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下的决定都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:01.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直像那个时候一样独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许也就不会现在这样乱想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 满善
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想干什么啊 优山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:17.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已经答应过春 不会再和他相见了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:21.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 那个春竟然为了这个文化祭 都彻夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 请给我两个红豆甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他看见我在这里出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会露出相当讨厌的表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是超级期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要为了这种事让我陪你来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知到你说的是真是假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:49.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗？ 我正准备回去 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的后院真是宽广呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:16.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接向谁问下路不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌向他人求助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:22.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都已经迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.41,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,山贤君 要一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说好给我们介绍女孩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是只鸡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,近来过得好么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 因为我很中意这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这到底在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个世上 有很多危险的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了安全起见 所以我做了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字就叫做 水谷雫……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把那种东西起名叫 人家的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 山贤你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在后院迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 佐佐原叫我们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么雫会和山贤在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰……碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.63,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要避开我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样逼迫女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.45,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们轮流拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.19,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我没有允许的就碰触你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,却让这个家伙随便碰你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:36.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是摆明了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:41.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以碰 但你不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我离开雫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哇啊 直接击中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.99,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,打到脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快道歉 春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.80,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什么呢 无脑男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 还不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？竟然要把错推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:05.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后绝对不允许……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入我半径两米之内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有生气、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:29.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:33.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样被春耍的团团转的自己真有点傻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:38.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那样 和不辨是非的小孩没区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,傲慢而且只考虑自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:42.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我还是无法丢下他不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这……这难道是 恋爱咨询？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女间的爱情是剪不断理还乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所谓Best Of Only One啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春选择和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为他不想孤单一人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:04.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:10.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是正好出现在他身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:16.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 你不相信春同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不想孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,理所当然会认为待在自己身旁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己来说是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 难道你对春没有这种感觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 夏目同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好冷淡啊 那个书呆女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:55.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 还不是因为山贤乱插手春的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？关我什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去吗？去安慰她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 还是在这多观察一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:11.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水你不相信春吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么事情会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:21.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的鼻子因为我被打成那样 我也很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,追究起来确实是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 真可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你讨厌了的话 春又要变成孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,又？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:36.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来告诉你吧 为什么你无法丢下那家伙不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:37.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你对他有所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的言行中也混有你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才会放不下春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己任性的期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却无法回应对方的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个残酷的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,水谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:58.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(944,526,952,227)\fad(0,700)\fs50\fn方正粗活意简体\c&H2E1EB9&\3c&HF6DC81&\pos(944,526)}刨\N\N冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不和我保持距离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法和你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是伤害到他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？难道是现在一个人觉得寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不巧 一直以来我都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没有觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨~蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,寂寞这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要有朋友之后才会感觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,优山先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:44.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:49.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？优山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,…痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！为什么那家伙会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识优山先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们兄弟俩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都在海明高中上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕优山先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 怎么会有我害怕的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…有点心理阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会毁了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,山贤同学 请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你可是一点都没有欲念哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:41.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…诶？ 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉…吉田同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！那个鳗鱼混蛋竟然敢违背约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:12.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？什么？之前说过的那个鳗鱼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指刚才那个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.63,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 今天到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我说喜欢你的话 你会觉得讨厌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我我该怎么回答？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得越是和雫说我喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,状况就会变得越来越糟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 就只好霸王硬上弓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说这件事啊 诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么一回事啊 作为当事人你也解释下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:56.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那么 如果我说我喜欢吉田同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊 这么平白无故的问我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不讨厌你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不是指这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…那个 怎么说好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是雌性追求喜欢的雄性的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种…那种是要做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.60,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 偷听别人说话不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是精彩的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.60,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,更像柏拉图式的那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:31.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩为什么会在这种地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小雫说了比较深入的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果被她断然拒之门外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是因为不想孤单一人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:02.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像我的心事 被看穿了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:07.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心就对小水说了责备她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得小水第一次 和我说这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:15.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 小夏目确实是生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家相互把火发出来就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们女孩子一旦吵架了 就全都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是给夏目朝子最后通牒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要取决于 你自己是否还想和她做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是我的第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想失去她！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 就是这种干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起！了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想主动和她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.54,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了！找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学你在做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.43,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你脾气这么倔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 有很多原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 棒球少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:58.81,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…和优山一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正好该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众都聚过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,切…啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打算闹事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:37.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真的怎么样都无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 真可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大岛同学 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:04.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起呢 我弟弟给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:10.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好 我有事找小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:15.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我正麻烦她带路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是山口先生家的贤二吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:31.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚春逃跑时落下的鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我还给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:33.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.19,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,收好 你的生意道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会喽 小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在这呢在这呢 让我好找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这和书呆女做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:52.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦 水谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:58.67,tk-default2,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑×N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.27,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这么郁闷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想清楚后再行动怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 反省一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我也一样是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是搞错事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不要两米了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:44.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 那个可以取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现订规则也是没意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我先去跟大岛道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要发现错误 想要改正并不是难事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:22.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目好心给我意见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:25.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的态度太没有诚意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事我想跟你说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:37.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是小水和春同学的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是没有关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 总算找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也差不多工作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 原来是雫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我要说的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才想做什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:08.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我想摸摸你的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 头发？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:18.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫的想法我实在不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上说没事看起来却相反
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然又说不让我靠近你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,进也不是退也不是 到底要我怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:30.02,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:39.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 春无论何时都是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,手好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:47.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直不去正面面对的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:52.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这么逼问 我也有想过的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.03,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会是这种心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的选择正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:06.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我会不会又喜欢你到 无法专心念书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:12.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 最后还是在学习中平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我一直是和学习战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:23.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样 不想再有那种感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想变得不能好好读书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:29.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不念书我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你突然干什么春！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:46.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像之前曾经这样过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:55.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边真实的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:06.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人感到舒服 却有点悲伤的安心感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:09.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天的我所不知道的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:13.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:13.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:18.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能再给我点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好考虑春的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:24.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,学会面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:26.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:27.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:31.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:22.02,next title1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:47.80,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,星の街路中　君と歩き町
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:54.97,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,笑った途端白い息が凍えそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:02.06,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,あ　どうして今日も冗談ばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:09.69,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,相変わらず微妙な距離もどかしくて切ないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:19.62,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,巡る巡る冬の夜は今年は　あ　高いね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:26.13,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,味方だって　寂さだって　何だか嬉しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:33.55,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,「今日が回りしよう」君から言わないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:41.01,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,これが恋か恋じゃないかどっちだって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:47.40,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でも喧嘩してもやっぱり君がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:54.70,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,降り出した雪に願いをかけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:24:03.10,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,あとちょっとこのままで二人きり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:47.80,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,繁星点点的街道上 与你漫步而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:54.97,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,欢笑间呵出的白色雾气似乎一瞬就会被冰冻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:02.06,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 今天你也总是说些玩笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:09.69,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间的微妙距离依然如此让人焦躁苦闷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:19.62,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,斗转星移今年的冬季 夜晚的天空很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:26.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有知己 就算会寂寞 仍有些莫名的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:33.55,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,「今天去哪里转转吧」你会不会说出这样的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:41.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,无论这是否是恋爱都没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:47.40,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算很笨拙就算会吵架只要有你在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:54.70,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向飘落的雪花许下心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:24:03.10,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样继续在二人世界多停留一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:10.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:11.96,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近却很冷淡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:13.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说血缘是不能违背的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:15.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说想违背也无济于事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.62,0:24:20.09,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我渐渐深以为然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:21.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
